              For which <m>x</m>-value(s) does <m>f(x)=1</m>?
              <ol marker= "A." cols="6">  
               
                <li> <m>-1</m></li>
                <li> <m>0</m></li>
                <li> <m>1</m></li>
                <li> <m>2</m></li>
                <li> <m>3</m></li>
                <li> <m>4</m></li> 
                
              </ol>
            </p>
          </statement>
